{"tid":936231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「 防彈少年團」台灣遇車禍 經紀公司聲明：成員平安","createTime":"2018-12-10T15:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T15:08:43.000Z","uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c53dbec00027811fcc15c879276017fdfaf0ca","tid":936231,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLkat3F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLkat3F.jpg&h=8027ddc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓團「防彈少年團」（BTS）周末連2天在在桃園國際棒球場舉辦「LOVE YOURSELF」巡演，吸引5萬人朝聖，然而昨（9日）演唱會結束後，傳出意外消息，成員在回飯店的車程中遇車禍，主辦單位LIVE NATION回應「因為今天車多，前方車子忽然煞車，導致藝人坐的保母車追撞上去，而後方的小黃也撞到保母車，但是否是粉絲車子他們不了解，之後藝人換車後已安全回到飯店，請粉絲放心」。<br />\n<br />\n有粉絲不放心，希望BTS所屬Big Hit娛樂回應，而今早他們也發出聲明，證實防彈少年團結束演出後，前往飯店途中發生擦撞意外，幸好情況輕微，「成員全體都沒有受傷，也安全地回到了飯店，對於今後的行程並無影響」，讓粉絲放心不少。而BTS今天搭專機離台。<br />\n<br />\n又防彈 又防撞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd20a3c527429e5433e910f6816d31aa832063f","tid":936231,"uid":52652,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:04:08.000Z","msg":"韓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed145142fc220210a6dcb4a9d244903166e18562","tid":936231,"uid":134521,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:06:09.000Z","msg":"死咗唔通又話你知咩 公司拿拿林搵過第二個整容做替身補上"},{"pid":"f130401c197ec2ccf4e16692fd0fa2fd7c885fc5","tid":936231,"uid":43061,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"咁都炒唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41136678a4992cf7ed552bc03489e4af275599f9","tid":936231,"uid":41508,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:08:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"974f08401564984c3e053be9850e55c4aafb904b","tid":936231,"uid":11598,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.c